      <title>在美联储做出决定之前，加密货币洗盘导致比特币跌破 58,000 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/bitcoin-slides-below-58000-rattled-by-tougher-fed-rate-outlook-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币周三下跌近 6%，4 月份创下了自 2022 年底以来的最差月度表现，原因是投资者在美联储稍后公布利率决定之前从加密货币中撤出资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/bitcoin-slides-below-58000-rattled-by-tougher-fed-rate-outlook-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 07:39:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
